data.title: Adult-Onset Leukoencephalopathy With Axonal Spheroids and Pigmented Glia
data.meta_description: Adult-Onset Leukoencephalopathy With Axonal Spheroids and Pigmented Glia - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides a review of adult-onset leukoencephalopathy with axonal spheroids and pigmented glia (ALSP), a rare neurodegenerative disorder. It summarizes the genetics, neuropathology, clinical manifestations, current treatments and lack thereof for ALSP. The review aims to establish a foundation for developing therapeutic strategies and clinical trials to address the unmet medical needs of ALSP patients.
